  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.sql.CallableStatement, java.sql.PreparedStatement, java.sql.Statement, java.sql.Wrapper, FirebirdCallableStatement, FirebirdPreparedStatement, FirebirdStatement, Synchronizable
    public class FBCallableStatement
extends AbstractCallableStatement
    JDBC 4.2 implementation of PreparedStatement interface.

    Contains methods specific to the JDBC 4.2 implementation, or exists if there are methods in higher JDBC versions that cannot be defined in JDBC 4.2.

    Author:
    David Jencks, Roman Rokytskyy, Steven Jardine, Mark Rotteveel
